name: Unidentified_Revwien_trader
content: This individual was a member of the Revwien species. Sometime prior to 22 BBY, it lived in the town of Mos Nytram on Tatooine. It auctioned to local resident Owen Lars a Zephyr-G swoop that was later used by Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker to track down and slaughter the Tusken Raiders that had captured his mother.
